      <title>消息人士称</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/credit-agricole-close-settling-french-dividend-tax-case-with-fine-source-says-2025-09-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据称，Credit Agricole SA的投资银行部门即将解决涉嫌避免扣除税款的股息票据交易的犯罪调查，这是一份接近此事的消息人士所说，该事务的消息人士说，法国信息的较早报告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/credit-agricole-close-settling-french-dividend-tax-case-with-fine-source-says-2025-09-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Sep 2025 16:09:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
